<p>Each radio button has one value. I want to add the values every time someone select a radio button. To select the right radio button 1 will be added and for wrong 0.5 will be subtracted. The final result will show in ov div.</p>  <pre><code>var app = angular.module('plunker', []);  app.controller('aCtrl', function($scope) { var v= 0 ; $scope.cal = function(){   $scope.rv.click();   v +=$scope.rv;   $scope.ov = JSON.stringify(v); };  }); </code></pre>  <p>Here is my plunker link  <a href="http://plnkr.co/edit/onjtGkkG0FiK4dOCmJfX?p=preview" rel="nofollow">http://plnkr.co/edit/onjtGkkG0FiK4dOCmJfX?p=preview</a></p>